<div class="content-box">
    <h2>{{ lang._('PondSec NDR') }}</h2>
    <p>{{ lang._('PondSec NDR analyzes firewall-visible network metadata. It does not replace endpoint detection and response.') }}</p>
    <p>{{ lang._('It cannot reliably detect local process manipulation, registry changes, memory injection, local file changes, or traffic that does not traverse this firewall.') }}</p>
    <p>{{ lang._('The default mode is monitor. Automatic blocking is disabled unless explicitly enabled by policy in a later response phase.') }}</p>
</div>
